{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_LightningRemove}}
'''A_LightningRemove'''<br />
(no parameters)

Clears the calling actor's lastenemy's own <tt>lastenemy</tt> field, and makes it explode. Does not affect the calling actor itself.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|LightningCeiling}} and derived classes.

[[Category:Decorate Hexen functions]] [[Category:Decorate Status change functions]] [[Category:Decorate Restricted functions]]{{DEFAULTSORT:LightningRemove}}
